OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fslowly dying out this evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. A cold
OL,9,Fnight with patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAfter a cold start the morning
OL,12,Fwill be dry and bright. Staying dry in
OL,13,Fthe afternoon but clouding over.
OL,14,FPatchy rain spreading south in the
OL,15,Fevening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry,
OL,18,Fbright and cold on Monday. Sunny
OL,19,Fspells and a few showers on Tuesday
OL,20,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
